<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA524_07_IH_0006_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema524_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema524_07_ih_0006">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="6" class="is_star" lang="y">재활용품을 재윤이는 2.65 kg만큼 모아 분리배출 했고, 서하는 재윤이가 모은 재활용품의 1.4배만큼 모아 분리배출 했습니다. 서하가 분리배출 한 재활용품은 몇 kg인지 식을 쓰고 답을 구해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box justify_center gap_40">
          <div class="img">
            <img src="../../common_practice/img/EMA524_07_IH/0006_img.png" alt="" />
            <span class="txt1" lang="y">캔</span>
            <span class="txt2" lang="y">유리</span>
            <span class="txt3" lang="y">플라스틱</span>
            <span class="txt4" lang="y">종이</span>
          </div>
          <div class="div flex dir_col gap_20">
            <div class="flex align_end gap_10">
              <span class="label_gray" lang="y">식</span>
              <div class="input_wrap_underline align_center">
                <div class="input_wrap answer1"><math-field data-answer-single="2.65×1.4"></math-field></div>
                =
                <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="3.71"></math-field></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex align_end gap_10">
              <span class="label_gray" lang="y">답</span>
              <div class="input_wrap_underline align_end">
                <div class="input_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="3.71"></math-field>
                </div>
                &nbsp;
                <span>kg</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">(서하가 분리배출 한 재활용품의 무게)=(재윤이가 분리배출 한 재활용품의 무게)×1.4=</p>
                <p>2.65×1.4=3.71 (kg)</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- <div class="buttons_solve">
                  
              </div> -->
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
